{"paragraphs":[{"cues":[{"time":1000,"text":"Why grow homes? Because we can."},{"time":4000,"text":"Right now, America is in an unremitting state of trauma."},{"time":7000,"text":"And there's a cause for that, all right."},{"time":9000,"text":"We've got McPeople, McCars, McHouses."},{"time":12000,"text":"As an architect, I have to confront something like this."}]},{"cues":[{"time":15000,"text":"So what's a technology that will allow us"},{"time":17000,"text":"to make ginormous houses?"},{"time":19000,"text":"Well, it's been around for 2,500 years."},{"time":22000,"text":"It's called pleaching, or grafting trees together,"},{"time":25000,"text":"or grafting inosculate matter into one contiguous, vascular system."},{"time":28000,"text":"And we do something different"},{"time":30000,"text":"than what we did in the past;"},{"time":32000,"text":"we add kind of a modicum of intelligence to that."},{"time":34000,"text":"We use CNC to make scaffolding"},{"time":36000,"text":"to train semi-epithetic matter, plants,"},{"time":38000,"text":"into a specific geometry"},{"time":40000,"text":"that makes a home that we call a Fab Tree Hab."},{"time":43000,"text":"It fits into the environment. It is the environment."},{"time":45000,"text":"It is the landscape, right?"}]},{"cues":[{"time":47000,"text":"And you can have a hundred million of these homes,"},{"time":49000,"text":"and it's great because they suck carbon."},{"time":51000,"text":"They're perfect."},{"time":53000,"text":"You can have 100 million families, or take things out of the suburbs,"},{"time":56000,"text":"because these are homes that are a part of the environment."},{"time":59000,"text":"Imagine pre-growing a village --"},{"time":61000,"text":"it takes about seven to 10 years --"},{"time":63000,"text":"and everything is green."}]},{"cues":[{"time":66000,"text":"So not only do we do the veggie house,"},{"time":69000,"text":"we also do the in-vitro meat habitat,"},{"time":72000,"text":"or homes that we're doing research on now in Brooklyn,"},{"time":75000,"text":"where, as an architecture office, we're for the first of its kind"},{"time":78000,"text":"to put in a molecular cell biology lab"},{"time":81000,"text":"and start experimenting with regenerative medicine"},{"time":83000,"text":"and tissue engineering"},{"time":85000,"text":"and start thinking about what the future would be"},{"time":87000,"text":"if architecture and biology became one."}]},{"cues":[{"time":89000,"text":"So we've been doing this for a couple of years, and that's our lab."},{"time":92000,"text":"And what we do is we grow"},{"time":94000,"text":"extracellular matrix from pigs."},{"time":96000,"text":"We use a modified inkjet printer,"},{"time":98000,"text":"and we print geometry."},{"time":100000,"text":"We print geometry where we can make industrial design objects"},{"time":103000,"text":"like, you know, shoes, leather belts,"},{"time":105000,"text":"handbags, etc.,"},{"time":107000,"text":"where no sentient creature is harmed."},{"time":109000,"text":"It's victimless. It's meat from a test tube."},{"time":111000,"text":"So our theory is that eventually"},{"time":113000,"text":"we should be doing this with homes."}]},{"cues":[{"time":115000,"text":"So here is a typical stud wall,"},{"time":117000,"text":"an architectural construction,"},{"time":119000,"text":"and this is a section"},{"time":121000,"text":"of our proposal for a meat house,"},{"time":123000,"text":"where you can see we use fatty cells as insulation,"},{"time":125000,"text":"cilia for dealing with wind loads"},{"time":127000,"text":"and sphincter muscles for the doors and windows."}]},{"cues":[{"time":130000,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":133000,"text":"And we know it's incredibly ugly."},{"time":135000,"text":"It could have been an English Tudor or Spanish Colonial,"},{"time":138000,"text":"but we kind of chose this shape."},{"time":140000,"text":"And there it is kind of grown, at least one particular section of it."}]},{"cues":[{"time":143000,"text":"We had a big show in Prague,"},{"time":145000,"text":"and we decided to put it in front of the cathedral"},{"time":147000,"text":"so religion can confront the house of meat."},{"time":150000,"text":"That's why we grow homes. Thanks very much."}]},{"cues":[{"time":152000,"text":"(Applause)"}]}]}